trans-unit.source: Represents a field that displays navigation controls in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"></xref> control enable users to page through data.
trans-unit.target: Representa um campo que exibe os controles de navegação em um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager"> </xref> controle permitem que os usuários para a página de dados.

trans-unit.source: The NextPreviousPagerField class represents a field that displays navigation controls in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control.
trans-unit.target: A classe NextPreviousPagerField representa um campo que exibe os controles de navegação em um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>controle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>

trans-unit.source: These navigation controls can be used to page through data that are displayed by a control that implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IPageableItemContainer> interface, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> control.
trans-unit.target: Esses controles de navegação podem ser usados para ver os dados que são exibidos por um controle que implementa o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IPageableItemContainer>interface, como o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView>controle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ListView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.IPageableItemContainer>

trans-unit.source: The NextPreviousPagerField class provides buttons that enable users to navigate through the pages of data one page at a time, or to jump to the first or last page of data.
trans-unit.target: A classe NextPreviousPagerField fornece botões que permitem aos usuários navegar pelas páginas de dados uma por vez, ou para ir para a primeira ou última página de dados.

trans-unit.source: You can customize the appearance of the NextPreviousPagerField object by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonCssClass%2A> property to set the style of the buttons.
trans-unit.target: Você pode personalizar a aparência do objeto NextPreviousPagerField usando o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonCssClass%2A>propriedade para definir o estilo dos botões.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonCssClass%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A> property to choose the type of button that is displayed.
trans-unit.target: Você também pode usar o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>propriedade para escolher o tipo de botão é exibido.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>

trans-unit.source: The following table lists the available button types.
trans-unit.target: A tabela a seguir lista os tipos disponíveis de botão.

trans-unit.source: |Button type|Description| |-----------------|-----------------| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>|A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button> control.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>|An <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> control.| |<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>|A <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control.| You can hide a NextPreviousPagerField object in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> control by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField.Visible%2A> property to `false`.
trans-unit.target: | Tipo de botão | Descrição | |-----------------|-----------------| | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>| Um controle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>| Um controle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>. | | <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>| Um controle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>. | Você pode ocultar um objeto NextPreviousPagerField em um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager>controle definindo o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField.Visible%2A>propriedade `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField.Visible%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ButtonType>

trans-unit.source: You can also hide the individual buttons (the first-page, previous-page, next-page, and last-page buttons) by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowFirstPageButton%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowPreviousPageButton%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowNextPageButton%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowLastPageButton%2A> properties to `false`.
trans-unit.target: Você também pode ocultar os botões (os botões de primeira página, página anterior, próxima página e última página) definindo o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowFirstPageButton%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowPreviousPageButton%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowNextPageButton%2A>, e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowLastPageButton%2A>propriedades `false`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowLastPageButton%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowNextPageButton%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowPreviousPageButton%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ShowFirstPageButton%2A>

trans-unit.source: The NextPreviousPagerField control enables you to specify custom text for each button by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageText%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageText%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: O controle NextPreviousPagerField permite que você especifique o texto personalizado para cada botão usando o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageText%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageText%2A>, e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageText%2A>Propriedades.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageText%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A> property is set to `ButtonType.Image`, you must provide the URL to an image that will be displayed for the button.
trans-unit.target: Quando o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>estiver definida como `ButtonType.Image`, você deve fornecer a URL para uma imagem que será exibida para o botão.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can set images individually for each button by setting the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageImageUrl%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageImageUrl%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageImageUrl%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageImageUrl%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Você pode definir imagens individualmente para cada botão, definindo a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageImageUrl%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageImageUrl%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageImageUrl%2A>, e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageImageUrl%2A>Propriedades.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.LastPageImageUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.NextPageImageUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.PreviousPageImageUrl%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageImageUrl%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A> property is set to `ButtonType.Image`, the corresponding text property acts as the alternate text for the image.
trans-unit.target: Quando o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>estiver definida como `ButtonType.Image`, a propriedade de texto correspondente atua como o texto alternativo para a imagem.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, the text that is specified by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A> property is displayed as the alternate text for the first-page image button.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o texto que é especificado pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A>propriedade é exibida como o texto alternativo para o botão de primeira página de imagem.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.FirstPageText%2A>

trans-unit.source: In browsers that support tooltips, this text is also displayed as a tooltip.
trans-unit.target: Em navegadores que oferecem suporte a dicas de ferramenta, esse texto também é exibido como uma dica de ferramenta.

trans-unit.source: The buttons are disabled by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField> object when the function associated with the button cannot be performed.
trans-unit.target: Os botões são desabilitados pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField>objeto quando a função associada com o botão não pode ser executada.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField>

trans-unit.source: For example, when you are in the first page of data, the first-page and previous-page buttons are disabled.
trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, quando você estiver na primeira página de dados, os botões de primeira página e página anterior estão desabilitados.

trans-unit.source: By default, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField> object renders the disabled buttons by using the control type specified by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Por padrão, o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField>objeto renderiza os botões desabilitados usando o tipo de controle especificado pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField.ButtonType%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.NextPreviousPagerField>

trans-unit.source: It also sets the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebControl.Enabled%2A> property of the control to `false`.
